# to list & modify interfaces on host
ip link

## to view ip address to those interfaces
ip addr


## To set ip address to interfaces
ip addr add 192.168.1.10/24 dev etho

ip route

ip route add 192.168.1.0/24 via 192.168.2.1

cat /proc/sys/net/ipv4-forward

DNS:

etc/hosts is single source of truth
etc/resolv.conf is dns servers where it find ip address of all machines

if it has in both etc/hosts & etc/resolv.conf then it will take etc/host entry but that can changed /etc/nsswitch.conf

